<BaseLayout title="Gonzalo Reynoso | Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5 mt-28">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Full Stack Developer with experience in web application development. I have
    worked on various projects using a wide range of technologies, including
    JavaScript, React, TypeScript, Node.js, Angular, Express, SQL, and NoSQL. <br
    />I have experience in version control using Git, GitHub, Gitlab, Jira,
    Teams, Trello, and implementing Kanban and Scrum in development teams to
