      subtitle="From Oct 2024 to Present at Innevo, Santiago de Chile, Chile">
      I worked on a web application built with Angular, focusing on creating a
      dynamic and responsive user interface. My role involved developing modular
      components, integrating Angular Material for a cohesive design, and
      implementing advanced TypeScript practices. <br />
      The application interacts with various REST APIs, enabling efficient data handling
      and ensuring a seamless user experience. <br />
      • Angular Component Development: Built reusable and optimized Angular components,
      following best practices. <br />
      • Angular Material Integration: Implemented Angular Material to enhance user
      experience and visual consistency.<br />
      • Reactive Forms: Developed dynamic and custom-validated forms using Angular
      Reactive Forms.<br />
      • State Management and Services: Configured Angular services to handle business
      logic and share data between components.<br />
      • REST API Integration: Integrated external APIs using Angular’s HTTPClient
      for CRUD operations and data display.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Administrative & IT Analyst"
      subtitle="From Aug 2020 to Apr 2024 at Medicina Diagnóstica, Buenos Aires, CABA, Argentina">
      As an Administrative & IT Analyst at Medicina Diagnóstica, I focused on
      optimizing internal processes through the development of technological
      solutions, task automation, and data management. My work ranged from
      document digitization to customer service. <br />
      • Developed applications using Google Script to automate company payroll processes,
      optimizing data collection and financial processing. <br />
      • Implemented interactive dashboards with Power BI, enhancing administrative
      and financial data analysis in the healthcare sector. <br />
      • Designed and developed the laboratory’s official website using WordPress
      and MySQL, ensuring accurate and up-to-date information.<br />
      • Managed digital and physical documentation in the billing department, applying
      methodologies to improve data organization and accessibility.<br />
      • Provided customer service support, handling patient registration and delivering
      clinical test results with efficiency and accuracy.<br />
      • Managed invoicing, payment tracking, and employee payroll processing, ensuring
      a smooth administrative workflow.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

